    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition, offering a reliable and practical option for those who value performance over perfection. Mechanically, it is sound; the engine starts reliably, and it handles daily driving tasks without issue. However, the exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some fading in the clear coat. Inside, the cabin is clean but shows typical wear on the upholstery and high-touch surfaces. It is a solid, honest car that has been regularly serviced and is ready for continued use as a dependable commuter or work vehicle.",
