      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is recommended only for those seeking a dedicated project car or a donor for parts. The engine suffers from significant mechanical issues, including a knocking sound and heavy oil consumption, and the transmission shifts very harshly. Cosmetically, the body shows several large dents, peeling clear coat, and rust spots around the wheel wells, while the interior has torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. It is not currently roadworthy and will require a trailer for transport.",
