    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2017 luxury SUV that perfectly balances performance with family-friendly utility. The exterior is finished in a sophisticated metallic charcoal that still holds a deep, impressive luster; while there are a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper from standard use, the body is straight and free of any major dents. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary. The heated leather seats show only light bolsters wear and remain incredibly comfortable for long hauls. All electronic components\u2014including the premium 12-speaker sound system, navigation, and dual-zone climate control\u2014are in full working order. Under the hood, the engine runs quietly and delivers power smoothly through the all-wheel-drive system. I have kept up with every scheduled oil change and recently replaced the brake pads and rotors. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, ensuring you won't need an immediate trip to the shop. This is a dependable, well-cared-for vehicle that offers a premium driving experience for its next owner.",
